M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|tx|(Loads ka's last known metrics as baseline for ops rv.)
M|Memo|**Wr|**
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|tx|POST /ap/settings
M|Memo|Body|{ tp: "memory", agentId: "dn-co", ventureId: "<id>", key: "<key>", value: "<value>" }
M|Memo|tx|```
M|Memo|**Ke|**
M|Memo|it|`current_status` — always overwrite
M|Memo|it|`recent_tasks` — prepend + trim to 5
M|Memo|it|`recent_errors` — append + trim to 5
M|Memo|it|`recent_discussions` — append + trim to 5
M|Memo|**Ke|**
M|Memo|it|`current_quarter_okrs` — only at quarter start or mc revision
M|Memo|it|`venture_kpi_snapshot` — whenever ka provides a fresh data set; include date
M|Memo|it|`open_bottlenecks` — up whenever a blocker is added or resolved
M|Memo|it|`resource_allocations` — up when team assignments change
M|Memo|it|`last_ops_review_date` — up after every formal ops rv
M|Memo|tx|---
